## Frequently Asked Questions

### Why can't VibEats find restaurants?

Please verify:

- Location Services are enabled.
- VibEats has permission to access your location.
- You have an internet connection.

### Can I change my BiteMeter rating?

Yes.

Open the restaurant page and select **Edit Rating**.

### Can I delete a review?

Yes.

Navigate to **My Ratings** and delete any review at any time.

### Why is my location incorrect?

Apple Maps determines nearby businesses using your device location.

If your location appears incorrect, verify Location Services are enabled.

### I found incorrect restaurant information.

Restaurant details are provided through Apple Maps. If business information is incorrect, it may be updated through Apple's business information process.

